PLANE WAVE NORMALLY INCIDENT ON WALL

&MESH ! 5mm resolution in z -- coarser than the EM mesh
  x_axis%coarse_grid = -0.025, 0.025
  x_axis%intervals = 5
  y_axis%coarse_grid = -0.025, 0.025
  y_axis%intervals = 5
  z_axis%coarse_grid = -0.1, 0.1
  z_axis%intervals = 40
/

&OUTPUTS
  output_t = 0.0, 1.0e-6
  output_dt = 1.0e-6
/

&NUMERICS /

&PHYSICS
  microwave_heating = T
  materials = 'dielectric', 'VOID'
/

&DIFFUSION_SOLVER
  abs_temp_tol = 0
  rel_temp_tol = 1e-4
  abs_enthalpy_tol = 0
  rel_enthalpy_tol = 1e-4
  verbose_stepping = T
/

### BODIES #####################################################################

&BODY
  surface_name = 'from mesh file'
  mesh_material_number = 1
  material_name = 'dielectric'
  temperature = 300.0
/

### BOUNDARY CONDITIONS ########################################################

&THERMAL_BC
  name = 'adiabatic'
  type = 'flux'
  face_set_ids = 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6
  flux = 0.0
/

### EM HEATING #################################################################

&EM_MESH ! 2mm resolution in z
  x_axis%coarse_grid = -0.025, 0.025
  x_axis%intervals = 5
  y_axis%coarse_grid = -0.025, 0.025
  y_axis%intervals = 5
  z_axis%coarse_grid = -0.1, 0.1
  z_axis%intervals = 100
/

&MICROWAVE_HEATING
  frequency = 2.45d9
  prop_change_threshold = 0.6
/

&FDME_SOLVER
  !use_mixed_form = T
  solver_type = 'minres'
  precon_type = 'ssor'
  rel_tol = 1e-12
  max_iter = 100000
  ssor_num_cycles = 2
  ssor_omega = 0.9
  print_level = 2
  graphics_output = T
/

Open artificial boundary. This should introduce the right moving
wave and pass the reflected left moving wave.

&ELECTROMAGNETIC_BC
  name = 'left open boundary'
  type = 'robin'
  face_set_ids = 5
  alpha = (0.0,51.3482)
  !g = (0.0, 0.0) (0.0, 102.6964) (0.0, 0.0)
  g = (0.0, 0.0) (-93.6689, 42.1034) (0.0, 0.0)
/

Reflecting wall
&ELECTROMAGNETIC_BC
  name = 'wall'
  type = 'pec'
  face_set_ids = 6
/

x-normal symmetry planes: nxH=0 on side set 1, 2
This is the default BC -- no need to specify

y-normal symmetry planes: nxE=0
&ELECTROMAGNETIC_BC
  name = 'y=const'
  type = 'pec'
  face_set_ids = 3, 4
/

### MATERIALS ##################################################################

### STUFF ###

&MATERIAL
  name = 'dielectric'
  density = 100.0
  specific_heat = 100.0
  conductivity = 1.0
/

